      "title": "Giant cycle rally in Yali",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A bicycle rally in Jaffna demanding the resignation of the President and Prime Minister. It was carried out in front of Central Bus Stand.",
        "from University of Jaffna, Jaffna. It started towards the city at 10 am today.",
        "Jaffna. The rally was organized by district mass organizations, trade unions, political parties and public organizations.",
        "The said rally went in front of Jaffna Central Bus Stand and gathered there and engaged in vigilance. (R)"
      ],
